Steps to get Bllip Parser
==========================

 1. cd $HOME_anu_test/Parsers/bllip-parser
 2. Run the below command to get the bllip parser
	git clone https://github.com/BLLIP/bllip-parser.git
 3. check the g++ version  :
	g++ --version
 4. if version < 4.7 then update g++ to 4.7
		(OR)
    Modify the below line in Makefile
	CXXFLAGS ?= $(CFLAGS) -Wno-deprecated -std=c++11
			as
	CXXFLAGS ?= $(CFLAGS) -Wno-deprecated -std=c++0x
 5. sh compile.sh
 6. cd $HOME_anu_test
 7. shell_scripts/remove_out-files.sh
 8. shell_scripts/anu_compile.sh


To Run Anusaaraka :
==================

Anusaaraka_bllip_parser.sh  <file_name>
